The phylogenetic analysis of NA sequences from Yucatan and Mexico showed a similar topology to the HA tree. Viruses from Yucatan grouped together but separated from viruses from other regions of Mexico, and viruses with the resistance mutation also grouped in a separate branch (

  S4 Fig
 ). Viruses from Yucatan showed close relationship to viruses isolated from South and Central America as well as North America, suggesting that A(H1N1)pdm09 viruses circulating in Yucatan were probably introduced from these regions and not from viruses circulating in central/north Mexico.
